description: The ever-ornate Azucar is one of the most acclaimed taco stops on the streets of Dallas!Rated in the “10 Most Underrated Tacos” by Dallas Observer, “The Best Under-the-Radar Tacos Around Dallas” by Thrillist, and “Top Ten Rookie Food Trucks of the Year” by Mobile Cuisine, Azucar continues to win over foodie fans with their delicious selection of Latin American dishes. You’ll find mouthwatering items on their menu like Mayan tacos on fluffy fry bread, Cuban quesadillas, chicken chorizo sandwiches with chimichurri, and so much more. If you wish to delight in Dallas’ best kept secret, be sure to keep an eye out for Azucar!
name: Azucar
